Package de.travelbuddy.model.place.exception

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    DuplicatePlaceException
    Should be thrown if a place already exists
    InvalidLatitudeException
    Should be thrown if a latitude value is not in the bounds of -90 and 90
    InvalidLongitudeException
    Should be thrown if a longitude value is not in the bounds of -180 and 180
    PlaceNotFoundException
    Should be thrown if a Place could not be found
